{"name":"Identify Spell","type":"action","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>a creature or a trap or similar object within line of sight casts a spell. You must be aware of the casting.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> trained in Arcana, Nature, Occultism, or Religion</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You attempt to determine the spell being cast. The GM rolls a secret Arcana, Nature, Occultism, or Religion check, whichever matches the tradition of the spell being cast.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You correctly identify the spell and the level at which it was cast.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> You correctly identify the spell and its base level, but not the level at which it was cast.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>You fail to identify the spell.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You misidentify the spell as another spell entirely, of the GMâ€™s choice</p>"},"source":{"value":"The Counterspeller's Codex"},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.819,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["secret"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.8.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676500955271,"modifiedTime":1678495399979,"lastModifiedBy":"hX8oUWHCdmx9DlSz"},"_id":"TKgXxu00Ws2UP91l","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"QjWjFUGIba5gj6fb":3}}
{"name":"Caster's Gambit","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\">You </span><span dir=\"ltr\">designate a single enemy and challenge them to a </span><span dir=\"ltr\">duel. You must be able to see or hear them. They </span><span dir=\"ltr\">become your Opponent. </span><span dir=\"ltr\">You take a -1 circumstance penalty to your AC and </span><span dir=\"ltr\">saving throws against them, but gain a +1 </span><span dir=\"ltr\">circumstance bonus to attack rolls and save DCs </span><span dir=\"ltr\">against them. This challenge lasts until the end of the </span><span dir=\"ltr\">encounter or until you or your Opponent is reduced </span><span dir=\"ltr\">to 0 HP.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.819,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-02-27T15:59:25.460-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.7.4"}}},"traits":{"value":["concentrate"],"custom":""},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.8.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677531565463,"modifiedTime":1678495395757,"lastModifiedBy":"hX8oUWHCdmx9DlSz"},"_id":"sawxzPnhx7dRQ3aq","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"QjWjFUGIba5gj6fb":3}}
{"name":"Caster's Demand","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\">You call out to your enemy and demand they respond to your challenge. When you use @Compendium[the-counterspell-codex.actions.sawxzPnhx7dRQ3aq]{Caster's Gambit}, you can add the auditory and linguistic traits. If you do so, your Opponent makes a @Check[type:will|dc:resolve(@actor.system.attributes.spellDC.value)] save against your spell DC.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span dir=\"ltr\">Critical Success</span></strong> <span dir=\"ltr\">Your challenge fails and the </span><span dir=\"ltr\">target is immune for 1 minute.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span dir=\"ltr\">Success</span> </strong><span dir=\"ltr\">Your Opponent takes a -1 circumstance penalty </span><span dir=\"ltr\">to checks and DCs for actions not targeting you for 1 </span><span dir=\"ltr\">round.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span dir=\"ltr\">Failure</span> </strong><span dir=\"ltr\">As success, but it lasts for 1 minute.</span></p>\n<p><span dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Critical</strong> <strong>Failure</strong></span><strong> </strong><span dir=\"ltr\">As failure and your Opponent becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1}</span><span dir=\"ltr\">.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.827,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-03-11T23:21:43.345-05:00","version":{"schema":0.819,"foundry":"10.291","system":"4.8.3"}}},"traits":{"value":["concentrate","auditory","linguistic"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.the-counterspell-codex.actions.sawxzPnhx7dRQ3aq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.8.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677531565463,"modifiedTime":1678595117503,"lastModifiedBy":"pak6Kff4byfPtnVT"},"ownership":{"default":0,"pak6Kff4byfPtnVT":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"fHKNG1UfitijKHtU"}
